text: Oktyabrsk () is a rural locality (a village) in Alegazovsky Selsoviet, Mechetlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 394 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 27 km from Bolsheustyikinskoye, 15 km from Alegazovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mechetlinsky District
title: Oktyabrsk, Mechetlinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
